{"tid":2358822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網民google earth 見七年前離世父親","createTime":"2021-01-08T11:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:57:11.000Z","uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bf229c54cc8ab8c1992b35b2f6cba554a4c64f4","tid":2358822,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b4s9zDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb4s9zDS.png&h=3b1fe519&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N8GygSf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN8GygSf.png&h=508fd97a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港咁多高樓大厦可能難啲，但日本咁多低密度獨立屋，又有花園&hellip;&hellip;事源呢位日本網民因為疫情而留喺屋企，悶悶哋就用GoogleEarth返老家睇吓，佢就驚喜發現原來影到佢7年前離世嘅爸爸，而且行前啲仲見到行緊嘅媽媽&hellip;&hellip;佢出咗圖之後，原來好多人都搵到自己在生、或已離世嘅親人，仲有狗狗朋友嗰啲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nタムチンキ<br />\n@TeacherUfo<br />\nコロナでやる事ないからGoogleEarthで実家見に行ったら7年前に死んだ親父が写ってた。その先に人が居たから見に行ったら母ちゃんだった。一服しながら奥さんの帰りを待ってたんだな。無口だけど優しい親父だった。このままこの場所の写真更新しないで欲しいな。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/479802?fbclid=IwAR3WnqtMQj-Rff5uCrr4rMKF0y-pvmO9Q9TvK2uHYfcrwjlEjPQtloQkq44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameover.com.hk%2Fnews%2F479802%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3WnqtMQj-Rff5uCrr4rMKF0y-pvmO9Q9TvK2uHYfcrwjlEjPQtloQkq44&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=67cc1a4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameover.com.hk/news/479802?fbclid=IwAR3WnqtMQj-Rff5uCrr4rMKF0y-pvmO9Q9TvK2uHYfcrwjlEjPQtloQkq44</a>"},{"pid":"53f4db5639f75de19bf7c17985f24c9c9845e2fe","tid":2358822,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"香港好難"},{"pid":"7b75f2910675038e880e0bf9a18b4707e19ac634","tid":2358822,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ca984fc6505c1ba751f4d02126222bfd0f99766a","tid":235